        {
            "title": "美伊立場差距仍大 全球能源危機持續 川普：無論結果為何美國都贏了",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CkxN0BujFqtu1TmfOyhKVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/120c8fda2409f517d526ccd1bb62299e\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D%E4%BB%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E7%84%A1%E8%AB%96%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%83%BD%E8%B4%8F%E4%BA%86-093002690.html",
